<h4 id="layout">Layout</h4>
<ol>
  <li>prefix+ space: change the layout from horizontal to vertial</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="session-operation">Session Operation</h4>

<ul>
  <li>exit current session:  prefix+d <font color="red">é€€å‡ºè¯¥sessionåï¼Œè¯¥sessionæ‰”åœ¨åå°è¿è¡Œ</font></li>
  <li>check out all sessions: tmux ls</li>
  <li>re-enter session: tmux attach -t session-name</li>
  <li>create a session with specific name: tmux new -s name</li>
  <li>rename a session: tmux rename-session -t 3 paper</li>
</ul>

<h5 id="session-switch">Session Switch</h5>
<ol>
  <li>prefix+w :the shortcut key of vim plugin nerdtree is also prefix+w</li>
</ol>
