<h4 id="plugin">plugin</h4>

<h4 id="tmux-plugin-manager">Tmux Plugin Manager</h4>

<p>Just as the name noted, this is plugin is used to manage plugins of tmux</p>

<h4 id="tmux-resurrect">tmux-resurrect</h4>
<p>key bindings</p>
<ul>
  <li>prefix + Ctrl-s -save</li>
  <li>prefix + Ctrl-l -restore</li>
</ul>

